  m_text: 'From: Your Boss



    Subject: Welcome, New Manager!



    Body:



    Hello
    Newbie!



    First of all, I''d like to congratulate you once again on your
    brand new position as a Zoo Manager! We''re so happy to have you as a part of
    our team. To get you started, we''ve arranged for the transfer of (SINGULAR ANIMAL
    NAME HERE) to your property. As a part of the onboarding process, we''d like
    to see you provide it with a suitable habitat in your facility. Please note that
    successful completion of the onboarding process will provide you with further
    funding for your endeavors.



    We look forward to hearing back from you about
    your success!



    Your Boss'
